      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·013.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">吉日.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吉日維戊，既伯既禱。田車既好，四牡孔阜。升彼大阜，從其羣醜。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>A lucky day was wu,
And we sacrificed on it to the Ruler of horses, and prayed.
Our hunting carriages were good;
The team for each was in fine condition.
We would ascend the greatest heights,
And pursue the herds of the game.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-nanyoujiayu-013__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
