      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·013.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">吉日.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吉日庚午，既差我馬。獸之所同，麀鹿麌麌。漆沮之從，天子之所。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>A lucky day was geng-wu.
We had selected our horses;
The haunts of the animals,
Where the does and stags lay numerous,
The grounds by the Qi and the Ju, --
That was the place for the son of Heaven to hunt.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-nanyoujiayu-013__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
