      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·013.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">吉日.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>瞻彼中原，其祁孔有。儦儦俟俟，或羣或友。悉率左右，以燕天子。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>We looked to the midst of the plain,
Where the animals were large and abundant,
Now rushing about, now waiting together,
Here in threes, there in twos.
We led on all our attendants,
To give pleasure to the son of Heaven.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
